me and\nevent-based) with a significantly smaller model size.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Sep 2022 21:40:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 1 Feb 2023 22:10:17 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 1 Mar 2023 12:52:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-02"}
