 These results demonstrate that in-situ biased 4D-STEM enables a\nbetter understanding of the electrical properties of semiconductor p-n\njunctions with nm-scale resolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Sep 2022 11:32:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-28"}
