 from\nthe black hole ranging between 10^11 and 10^13 cm. Similar outbursts from\nlow-mass X-ray binaries might be detectable in the near future with upcoming\ninstruments such as CTA.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Sep 2022 15:16:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 6 Oct 2022 12:27:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-07"}
