 the\nmiddle of the century to remain constant for the next 50 years, apart from the\nmodulation due to the solar cycle.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Sep 2022 09:59:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-12"}
